profile_positions.description:
Sea Point Offshore Services provides manpower contracting and recruitment services to support manpower on projects. Company's core service is in the provision of high calibre and experienced professionals to the Oil & Gas, Petrochemical, Power Generation and Civil and other related industries. 

Key Responsibilities: 

Organisation & Management 
•	Build the organisation from start-up to running business;
•	Create an annual business development plan and do monthly and quarterly follow up;
•	Prepare quarterly management reports on business growth.

Leadership, training & development
•	Lead, manage and train a team of recruitment, back-office and payroll executives;
•	Hold performance and assessment interviews annually with every employee.

Sales
•	Offer payroll services to MENA Global Recruitment’s existing clients in order to serve clients better and grow business; 
•	Build a network of new payroll clients in order to increase revenue; 
•	Create and give business presentation to companies in the Oil & Gas Industry.

Recruitment
•	Responsible for clear and up to date job descriptions online;
•	Responsible for personnel recruitment and selection;
•	Responsible for taking interviews;
•	Responsible for drawing up contracts;
•	Responsible for hiring personnel and inform payroll department for further hiring procedure.
